==English==

===Etymology===
* First attested in the 1610s.
* {{sense|exactness}} First attested in the 1650s.
* From {{der|en|la|accūrātus|t=done with care}}, perfect past participle of {{m|la|accūrō|t=take care of}}; from {{m|la|ad-|t=to, towards, at}} + {{m|la|cūrō|t=take care}}, from {{m|la|cūra|t=care}}.
* See {{l|en|cure}}.

